{"tid":230992,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[hehe] 愛·無能","createTime":"2017-05-05T17:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T04:38:25.000Z","uid":19900,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4a6f7ae58053bd683891efa23b15a97ba91733","tid":230992,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"世上有一種人，他們拼命尋覓愛，卻不懂如何去愛；他們渴望得到愛，卻害怕受到傷害，我稱他們為「愛無能」。"},{"pid":"86cbfdc0167bc15e255ea3d942b7ddfa4cfbecd0","tid":230992,"uid":7538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053f67ce50ea740bf2e7965e813be492b071484e","tid":230992,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:32:39.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"8a57df9daaec12a0da62a2e9bb32c001af618724","tid":230992,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e7dfc58a8b6615d021f4414f630cb812f3116d","tid":230992,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8ad1b56b7ccea9fe5429d583f3b23561c30c6a","tid":230992,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>hi</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nstatus?"},{"pid":"d3e09e136b0f90c6b0ea9707a79231c410673c40","tid":230992,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hi</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nstatus?</blockquote><br />\nAny pic?"},{"pid":"41bd7167e77c79c4c0865bbf965e8ee0609dc6e4","tid":230992,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hi</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nstatus?</blockquote><br />\nAny pic?</blockquote><br />\npmed"},{"pid":"727c4452f2d1ea2314d680721b71016949256887","tid":230992,"uid":19900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"HH:「ptbf?」<br />\n                                     「ys」:Hey<br />\n<br />\nHayden，文志希，一個二十歲出頭，同一般男仔差唔多嘅廢青，自從畢咗業之後佢就一直做各式各樣嘅散工，除咗7仔、m記、炒散，仲有就係而家討論得火紅火熱嘅兼職伴侶，即係ptbf。<br />\n<br />\nHH:「$300 ok?」<br />\n                             「no 700」:Hey<br />\nHH:「forget it」<br />\n<br />\n日上三竿，陽光透過窗簾照射到廢青臉上。交易拉倒，阿希感覺有d頹，四舊水？街邊d雞都唔做你生意啦！佢心諗⋯<br />\n<br />\n的而且確，ptbf要做嘅嘢，隨時麻煩過雞好多，陪行街、食飯、睇戲，足足花你一日嘅時間，仲要對住一個無感情嘅人扮到好boyfriendable，真係少d心力都做唔到，但呢樣嘢對阿希嚟講，其實唔難。<br />\n<br />\n各大交友apps幾乎都可以搵到阿希嘅身影，但佢好少會喺apps搵客，一嚟嗰度嘅人搵fun多，二嚟就算有多數都係對來自北方嘅大隻鴨仔有性趣，所以apps對於阿希嚟講，都只係一個搵炮友嘅平台。<br />\n<br />\n阿希從來都唔會直接用自己個樣做頭像，通常都係遮半面、背影之類，但都總係會有班人主動埋嚟hi，而呢班就係阿希嘅主要目標，雖然合心水嘅人係會比較少，佢似乎係願者上鉤派。<br />\n<br />\n被&quot;彈鐘&quot;嘅阿希唔知係心有不甘定係無聊得滯，佢再次開apps，每次開親佢都係萬無目的咁碌吓碌吓，連佢自己都唔知為乜。廿其實玩開嘅人都知，apps入面嘅人好多都奇撚怪怪，不論係外表定內裡，但有一個人，阿希對佢並唔抗拒，佢哋傾嘅野上至黃色話題，下至閒話家常都有，遺獨係大家都未見過對方嘅樣。<br />\n<br />\n每次開apps佢都會回覆咗阿希講嘅嘢，久而久之每日一覆就成為咗佢哋嘅慣性溝通方式，或者呢個就係阿希玩apps嘅主要原因。<br />\n<br />\nLLJ:嘩 甘你都好爽姐😦<br />\n       出街食飯睇戲唔洗錢<br />\n<br />\n阿希無耐前已經同咗佢講自己嘅兼職，<br />\n<br />\n                     爽條春！岩岩俾人彈鐘:Hey<br />\nLLJ:甘我包你 開個價😏"},{"pid":"6ae084b3c2deb19da43bb3959dfc0c1790b5d5f2","tid":230992,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"唔洗錢 ok?"},{"pid":"82330bdf36665e7024efa34183d1416e8624a6c5","tid":230992,"uid":19900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗錢 ok?</blockquote><